ve technology and customer service. Our love for fashion and dedication to our customers defines all we do. Our goal is to be the #1 online fashion retailer in Asia, and we need talented, committed and passionate individuals to help us get there. At ZALORA, we cultivate a dynamic environment, bringing together an unrivaled pool of talent from across Asia and the world, combining a wealth of local and international knowledge. The ZALORA values: Passionate
We are passionate about fashion, and about our customers. We are consistently motivated by our desire to bring high-street fashion to all corners of Asia, and we work tirelessly to provide the best experience for our customers. Innovative
As the leaders in fashion e-commerce in this region, we believe that continuously enhancing and redefining our product offering is key to moving ZALORA forward. We are continuously seeking new and innovative ways to do things, and believe in bringing new ideas to the table. Responsive and Adaptive
We are responsive and adaptive to the market we are in and changes going on around us in both fashion and technology. We adapt our offering to best fulfil the needs of each country, taking into account culture, socio-economic status and the overall climate in each country ZALORA operates in.Similar jobsSingaporePosted 1 day agoSingaporePosted 25 days agoSingaporePosted 21 days agoSingaporePosted 26 days agoSingaporePosted 21 days agoSingaporePosted 17 days agoSingaporePosted 1 day agoSingaporePosted 29 days agoSingaporePosted 7 days agoSan Francisco Bay AreaPosted 5 days agoThis is a preview of the Senior Software Engineer - iOS job at ZALORA Southeast Asia. To view the full job listing, join LinkedIn - its free!Join LinkedIn - its free!People also searchedPeople also viewedSingaporePosted 4 days agoSingaporePosted 10 days agoSingaporePosted 6 days agoSingaporePosted 7 days agoLondon, United KingdomPosted 4 days agoSingaporePosted 6 days agoSingaporePosted 4 days agoSingaporePosted 7 days agoAmsterdam Area, NetherlandsPosted 12 days agoSan Francisco Bay AreaPosted 11 days ago
